  <h1><b>Cookie Policy.</b></h1>
  <p>This Cookie Policy explains how our afrinimals website uses cookies and similar technologies to manage your session and improve your experience.</p>
  <h2><b>1. What Are Cookies?</b></h2>
  <p>Cookies are small text files that are stored on your device when you visit a website. They help websites remember certain information about your visit, such as your preferences or session status.</p>
  <h2><b>2. What We Use. </b></h2>
  <p>We only use essential technologies such as <b>local storage</b> and <b>session data</b> for the following purposes:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>To enable users to connect their TON wallet via TonConnect.</li>
    <li>To remember the connected wallet session between page reloads.</li>
    <li>To maintain security and prevent abuse.</li>
  </ul>
  <h2><b>3. No Tracking or Analytics. </b></h2>
  <p>We do not use any third-party tracking, advertising, or analytics cookies and if we to include so we shall include it here.</p>
  <h2><b>4. Consent.</b></h2>
  <p>Because we only use essential technologies, your continued use of the site is considered consent to this use. You do not need to provide additional cookie consent.</p>
 <h2><b>5. How to Control Cookies. </b></h2>
  <p>If you'd like to delete or block local storage or cookies, you can do so through your browser settings. However, this may affect the functionality of the wallet connection.</p>
